title: Redfall Is A Truly Awful Video Game...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Redfall, a game by Arkane and Microsoft that sets the level of innovation back to the days of early Xbox 360/PS3 levels of gameplay. This is a game that should have taken over 2 years extra of development time and released in a state that is quite literally unfinished. Thanks for watching!
